35:28.000 --> 35:36.000
It can be used, but the next day it should be restored.

35:36.000 --> 35:46.000
Thus, within the turnover, this amount should be on the enterprise's account.

35:46.000 --> 35:53.000
The enterprise works with it, actively uses it, and it is restored 25 times per year.

35:53.000 --> 35:57.000
It is restored 2 times per month.

35:57.000 --> 36:03.000
The amount of cash assets is spent for 15 days.

36:03.000 --> 36:07.000
