36:09.000 --> 36:13.000
And at the end of the cycle, it should be restored and spent again.

36:13.000 --> 36:18.000
Thus, we have determined the minimum amount of cash assets,

36:18.000 --> 36:26.000
which should be on the enterprise's account and used to pay the current payments.

